column2: SELECT  b.*,a.ra as sdss_ra, a.dec as sdss_dec, a.z as sdss_z,a.snMedian_r as sdss_sn_r, a.plate as sdss_plate, a.mjd as sdss_mjd, a.fiberID as sdss_fiberID into mydb.galpair_A1#_sdss_dr1#new from  mydb.galpair_A1#_sdss as b   CROSS APPLY  dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(b.ra_A,b.dec_A,#) as c   join DR1#.specObjAll as a on a.bestObjID=c.ObjID   where b.z_A=a.Z
